Specific Bundle - 
⛇☃︎ Winter Wonderland ☃︎⛇
The Winter Wonderland holiday bundle begins with a sophisticated stay at the Chalet Fantasia hotel, situated in a sunny and very peaceful location and with an amazing view of the most iconic Matterhorn.
